name: Chef Martin Yan
chefs-bio: Martin Yan was born in Guangzhou, China, and began cooking at the age of 12. His father was in the restaurant business and Yan picked up the culinary arts through the family. He went to college in Hong Kong to earn a degree in culinary arts.
